{
  "stem": "15721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I was about eight years old, I remember an incident.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was going home from school and there was a group of-- f boys with whom I played in a backyard or out on the street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of them was the superintendent's son, for instance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- there were not Jewish, they were all non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I come home and they-- they're waylaying me and they're beating me up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I finally came to, I said, what's gotten into you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, well, we just learned that you killed Christ-- that you killed Christ.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must say to you, that left a profound impact on me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went up to my father and I said, what is this business about me killing Christ?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember having done it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so my father explained to me that in so much of Christianity, there was this-- at that time-- teaching which has now been declared to be false by the Second Vatican Council that the Jews were responsible for the death of Jesus.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Second Vatican Council in the great document Nostra aetate in 1965 declared that teaching to be false and forbade for Roman Catholics in the future to-- to teach and believe in that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in those days, it was not only taught, it was believed in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm completely convinced that it was this particular story that made the Jews responsible for Jesus' death that is the-- the single most powerful seed out of which all anti-Jewish feeling and later anti-Semitism sprouted.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got beat up then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were other incidents in-- in school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the only one that was circumcised, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
